WEBVTT

00:00:02.323 --> 00:00:04.477
DVADTSAT' DEVYATOYE MARTA

00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:07.442
TYSYACHA DEVYAT'SOT DEVYANOSTO VOS'MOY GODA

00:00:07.442 --> 00:00:09.307
INTERV'YUIRUYEMYY

00:00:09.307 --> 00:00:11.357
KHATSKELIS LEMKHENAS

00:00:11.357 --> 00:00:14.757
INTERV'YUYERSHA ROZA BELIAUSKIENE

00:00:14.757 --> 00:00:16.841
VILNIUS LITVA

00:00:16.841 --> 00:00:18.275
YAZYK YIDISH

00:00:18.275 --> 00:00:20.914
KASETE NOMER VOSEM

00:00:22.287 --> 00:00:24.559
bite sheyn, zetst for.

00:00:24.801 --> 00:00:25.824
ya

00:00:26.067 --> 00:00:28.626
di lager, s'iz geven

00:00:28.648 --> 00:00:31.359
umgefer tsen, vayl ikh veys

00:00:31.973 --> 00:00:33.924
fun KAUFERING

00:00:34.352 --> 00:00:36.641
fun, iz geven

00:00:37.761 --> 00:00:41.754
i- mir veysn fun tsveytn bazunders fun dritn lager

00:00:42.418 --> 00:00:44.167
un fun tsentn.

00:00:44.460 --> 00:00:45.284
fun

00:00:45.284 --> 00:00:50.654
tsvishn, mir keyn mol gehert, nor s'iz geven a gevise bavegung. es flegt kumen

00:00:50.654 --> 00:00:53.764
me flegt iberheybn in mitn drinen a por mentshn

00:00:53.764 --> 00:00:57.262
a- nor etlekhe mentshn fun eyn lager in andern.

00:00:57.808 --> 00:00:58.966
eyn mol

00:00:59.530 --> 00:01:03.236
iz bay undz geven v- afile fun vayt

00:01:03.597 --> 00:01:06.729
gor nit fun di lagern iz geven a por.

00:01:09.688 --> 00:01:11.352
vu

00:01:12.979 --> 00:01:16.179
vu zayn, geven

00:01:16.320 --> 00:01:18.423
sh- shvere mentshn

00:01:18.784 --> 00:01:21.225
di az me f- tsu undz geb-

00:01:21.400 --> 00:01:23.554
gefirt tsu ENTLAUSUNG

00:01:24.150 --> 00:01:28.768
flegn unterzukhn un zen vu me ken vos tsuganvenen, tsunemen.

00:01:30.141 --> 00:01:35.251
mir hobn gevust az in lager dray iz do zeyer a guter

00:01:35.251 --> 00:01:37.256
shef a, a daytsh.

00:01:38.595 --> 00:01:40.968
lager tsvey iz oykh geven nit shlekht.

00:01:41.582 --> 00:01:43.516
lager fir iz geven

00:01:44.046 --> 00:01:45.575
oyf umtsukumen.

00:01:46.425 --> 00:01:49.018
mentshn vos hobn shoyn nit gehat keyn koyekh

00:01:49.362 --> 00:01:50.160
un

00:01:50.160 --> 00:01:52.429
flegn zikh betn aleyn

00:01:52.429 --> 00:01:55.922
az me zol zey shikn in lager fir. in lager fir

00:01:55.922 --> 00:01:58.791
flegn mentshn in meshekh fun a por vokhn

00:01:58.791 --> 00:02:03.395
oysgeyn, vayle dortn flegt men gebn nokh veyniker tsu esn.

00:02:04.482 --> 00:02:05.758
dos iz geven nor oyf

00:02:07.806 --> 00:02:11.529
eyn mol a khoydesh flegt kumen a daytsher dokter

00:02:13.155 --> 00:02:16.625
un m'hot gedarft durkhgeyn

00:02:17.678 --> 00:02:19.528
a kontrol far alemen.

00:02:23.331 --> 00:02:25.721
eyn tog bin ikh geven nit gerazirt

00:02:26.352 --> 00:02:28.236
un der vos iz gezesn

00:02:28.410 --> 00:02:32.167
in SCHREIBSTUBE vos ikh hob aykh gezogt vos hot mir gekent

00:02:32.528 --> 00:02:35.239
hot mir gezen nit keyn razirtn

00:02:36.426 --> 00:02:42.157
hot er gezogt "loyft shoyn un razirt zikh op." dortn iz geven a mentsh vos hot gerazirt

00:02:43.243 --> 00:02:46.477
"vayle s'vet kumen bald der dokter.

00:02:48.120 --> 00:02:51.185
az ir vet kumen mit a, mit aza oyszen

00:02:51.630 --> 00:02:53.632
vet men aykh avekshikn vu."

00:02:54.567 --> 00:02:57.097
i- un ikh hob, bin avek, un

00:02:57.097 --> 00:02:59.377
der vos hot mir razirt

00:02:59.377 --> 00:03:01.327
im fleg ikh do trefn.

00:03:01.327 --> 00:03:03.427
er lebt itst in Vilne.

00:03:04.202 --> 00:03:05.464
er hot nokh mir

00:03:05.464 --> 00:03:07.402
ongebotn, er vet kumen mikh

00:03:07.628 --> 00:03:09.478
shern un razirn

00:03:09.535 --> 00:03:12.600
vayle er flegt in, az ikh bin in krankn hoyz

00:03:12.640 --> 00:03:15.334
iz er dortn f- oykh flegt er kumen

00:03:15.525 --> 00:03:19.349
un flegt im tsuvarfn vos nit iz, a por lit.

00:03:19.626 --> 00:03:22.050
efsher gedenkt ir zayn nomen

00:03:23.608 --> 00:03:26.504
fun dem parikmakher? neyn.

00:03:31.810 --> 00:03:38.267
ikh hob im etlekhe mol gezen in, in kehile, in yidisher gemeynde

00:03:39.100 --> 00:03:43.177
un vi ikh zog aykh iz er, eyn mol hot er gev- zeyer

00:03:43.673 --> 00:03:45.433
gevelt ikh zol im

00:03:45.433 --> 00:03:49.134
nit andersh aynladn in shtub. er vet mir oprazirn

00:03:49.714 --> 00:03:52.323
hob ikh gezogt az ikh razir zikh aleyn. vos darf ikh

00:03:54.878 --> 00:03:55.766
ya.

00:03:56.886 --> 00:03:59.464
lager fir iz geven nor oyf, oyf

00:03:59.464 --> 00:04:00.814
oystsugeyn

00:04:00.814 --> 00:04:03.534
vayle dortn flegt men gebn nokh veyniker, un dos

00:04:03.534 --> 00:04:06.674
ken a mentsh nit oyshaltn in, mit aza bashpayzung.

00:04:08.901 --> 00:04:09.924
nu

00:04:12.124 --> 00:04:13.805
es iz gekumen a tog

00:04:15.516 --> 00:04:16.995
hot men geheysn

00:04:18.603 --> 00:04:21.145
fun tsenter, dos iz shoyn baym sof

00:04:22.553 --> 00:04:24.184
hot men fun tsenter

00:04:25.033 --> 00:04:28.284
geheysn kumen in DACHAU.

00:04:29.168 --> 00:04:31.170
der gantser lager zol geyn

00:04:31.446 --> 00:04:33.296
az s'vert do likvidirt.

00:04:38.112 --> 00:04:41.143
der farvalter fun sklad

00:04:41.942 --> 00:04:43.002
vu es

00:04:43.002 --> 00:04:45.683
ho- iz geven a bakanter mir.

00:04:47.848 --> 00:04:51.622
er hot gelebt in Kovne lebn, nit vayt fun mir

00:04:52.135 --> 00:04:55.909
hot er mir gegebn dray PORTYANKAs, un ikh hob UNK ⟨dos⟩ gut

00:04:57.231 --> 00:05:04.818
un a- arumgeviklt, es zol zayn varem di fis, vayl ikh hob nit gevust vu mir darfn geyn un vos ⟨m'vet⟩ geyn

00:05:06.782 --> 00:05:09.307
un mir zaynen avek.

00:05:10.815 --> 00:05:13.121
in eyn tog zaynen mir avek in

00:05:13.178 --> 00:05:15.011
tsenter DACHAU.

00:05:15.118 --> 00:05:17.491
ven iz dos geven, an erekh?

00:05:19.422 --> 00:05:21.036
nayntsn finf un fertsik.

00:05:21.970 --> 00:05:23.921
un dos iz ven geven

00:05:24.130 --> 00:05:27.144
s'iz geven kalt, tsi s'iz geven heys?

00:05:26.357 --> 00:05:27.937
neyn, dos iz geven

00:05:28.467 --> 00:05:31.431
dos iz geven, ikh ken aykh zogn afile a khoydesh.

00:05:32.584 --> 00:05:34.282
s'iz geven varshayndlekh

00:05:35.453 --> 00:05:36.527
april.

00:05:38.625 --> 00:05:39.918
in khoydesh april.

00:05:40.600 --> 00:05:45.521
iz in tsvey teg zaynen mir tsu fus avek in tsenter fun DACHAU.

00:05:45.730 --> 00:05:50.584
akhuts di PORTYANKAs, oyf di fis hot ir vos nit iz gehat?

00:05:51.636 --> 00:05:52.777
akhuts

00:05:55.500 --> 00:05:56.996
hiltserne

00:05:59.584 --> 00:06:01.755
nu UNK hiltserne shikh.

00:06:02.385 --> 00:06:07.441
un ot o, dos iz, in ot o di shikh hot ir gearbet dortn, tsi ir hot

00:06:06.098 --> 00:06:08.370
ya, vayle di, di

00:06:08.562 --> 00:06:10.513
undzere shikh hot men tsugenumen

00:06:11.093 --> 00:06:13.112
un mir hobn gehat nor hiltserne.

00:06:13.033 --> 00:06:15.676
un vos hot ir getrogn oyfn kerper?

00:06:22.382 --> 00:06:24.131
halt men ⟨nit⟩ ayn. mistome

00:06:26.500 --> 00:06:28.417
kh- dos dermon ikh UNK.

00:06:29.622 --> 00:06:32.586
alnfals, nit keyn kostyum

00:06:35.072 --> 00:06:36.922
ober a vos nit iz

00:06:38.295 --> 00:06:41.124
fun dest vegn nit keyn, nit keyn khalat.

00:06:44.860 --> 00:06:47.959
zaynen mir gekumen in tsenter fun DACHAU

00:06:50.007 --> 00:06:52.566
un ver hot gekukt oyf undz un ver darf undz

00:06:53.685 --> 00:06:55.653
un mir zaynen gekumen far nakht

00:06:56.942 --> 00:06:59.754
hobn mir ge- s'iz geven dokh ober

00:07:00.182 --> 00:07:01.559
april khoydesh

00:07:04.063 --> 00:07:06.706
hobn mir geshlofn oyf, oyf der erd.

00:07:07.202 --> 00:07:08.225
vu?

00:07:08.181 --> 00:07:09.390
in DACHAU.

00:07:09.413 --> 00:07:12.225
nor in a gebayde?

00:07:11.742 --> 00:07:13.524
neyn, in droysn.

00:07:15.133 --> 00:07:17.172
un oyf morgn in der fri

00:07:17.172 --> 00:07:19.076
dos iz geven der sof shoyn.

00:07:19.723 --> 00:07:21.320
oyf morgn in der fri

00:07:21.951 --> 00:07:24.386
hot mir, hot men zikh oysgeshtelt

00:07:24.386 --> 00:07:29.837
di vos hobn in tsentral DACHAU ge- UNK ⟨di arestantn⟩

00:07:29.837 --> 00:07:31.372
iz geven forgeshtelt

00:07:31.372 --> 00:07:33.284
kh'veys vifl felker fun

00:07:33.291 --> 00:07:37.571
iz geven frantsoyzn un s'iz geven englender un s'iz geven polyakn un s'iz geven

00:07:38.185 --> 00:07:40.204
yederer loyt der

00:07:40.328 --> 00:07:41.705
natsyonalitet.

00:07:43.264 --> 00:07:46.565
un m'hot zey gemeldet az DACHAU vert likvidirt.

00:07:47.263 --> 00:07:49.619
dos heyst, Hitler hot shoyn gehat farshpilt

00:07:51.010 --> 00:07:52.168
un

00:07:53.710 --> 00:07:55.071
zey kenen

00:07:55.161 --> 00:07:57.773
in tsentraln DACHAU iz yeder

00:07:57.773 --> 00:08:00.099
yedern's kostyum un yedern's

00:08:00.325 --> 00:08:01.874
shikh iz geven

00:08:01.874 --> 00:08:03.019
gehangen.

00:08:03.717 --> 00:08:07.423
az yederer ken tsunemen zayn kostyum un ze- zayne shikh.

00:08:11.007 --> 00:08:15.321
nu, i- iz, hobn zey gemeldet az zey

00:08:16.153 --> 00:08:17.952
zey veln vern fray

00:08:18.111 --> 00:08:20.653
ober undz hot men keyn zakh nit gemeldet.

00:08:21.486 --> 00:08:23.305
undz hot men oysgeshtelt

00:08:23.305 --> 00:08:24.433
oyf morgn.

00:08:25.468 --> 00:08:26.891
m'hot gegebn yedn

00:08:26.891 --> 00:08:30.727
a lebele broyt, dos iz a kilo mit tsvey hundert gram

00:08:32.927 --> 00:08:34.996
kh'veys nit tsi m'hot gegebn nokh vos.

00:08:35.205 --> 00:08:39.823
dos dermon ikh nokh nit. ken zayn az m'hot nokh vos ⟨undz⟩ gegebn epes a kleynikeyt, nit keyn

00:08:41.095 --> 00:08:43.283
un mir zoln geyn in a marsh.

00:08:46.933 --> 00:08:48.817
hot men undz ongehoybn firn.

00:08:50.460 --> 00:08:52.985
nit mir hobn gevust vu mir geyen, un

00:08:53.650 --> 00:08:54.574
un s-

00:08:54.574 --> 00:08:55.989
s'kumt bay der nakht

00:08:56.147 --> 00:08:58.908
iz lebn a vald shtelt men zikh op.

00:08:59.050 --> 00:09:00.782
"dort vet ir ibernekhtikn."

00:09:02.830 --> 00:09:04.342
gefirt hot men undz

00:09:05.665 --> 00:09:07.026
alts hekher

00:09:07.082 --> 00:09:08.696
mir zaynen gekumen

00:09:10.407 --> 00:09:13.101
dortn iz mistome geven di Alpn, ikh veys nit vos.

00:09:13.123 --> 00:09:15.142
mir zaynen shoyn geven gants hoykh.

00:09:15.925 --> 00:09:17.803
nit oyf di hekhste

00:09:17.803 --> 00:09:19.951
nor mir g- zaynen geven hoykh.

00:09:21.882 --> 00:09:25.726
undz hot m- hot men gefirt, arumgeringlt, zaynen mir geven mit

00:09:25.726 --> 00:09:27.090
S.S.nikes

00:09:27.990 --> 00:09:31.359
oyf mototsiklen, oyf velosipedn

00:09:31.652 --> 00:09:33.570
ale bavofnte

00:09:36.613 --> 00:09:39.437
un mir hobn nit gevust tsi me firt dos oyf

00:09:39.437 --> 00:09:42.395
tsu shisn oder, oder tsu

00:09:43.532 --> 00:09:45.905
ikh bin khoyshed az zey hobn oykh nit gevust

00:09:46.705 --> 00:09:48.403
dos v- vayl ikh veys nit

00:09:49.135 --> 00:09:50.192
m'hot gefirt

00:09:50.704 --> 00:09:53.347
un m'hot undz arayngefirt in di Alpn

00:09:53.877 --> 00:09:57.870
nit in di hekhste Alpn, ober in Alpn gebit, in der heykh.

00:09:59.547 --> 00:10:01.923
un in der nakht fun ershtn UNK

00:10:01.923 --> 00:10:06.611
UNK oyf, oyf, flegt zikh opshteln bay a vald oyf tsu nekhtikn

00:10:07.174 --> 00:10:08.450
fregt mir a

00:10:09.334 --> 00:10:12.315
a Klaypeder yid, fregt er "LEMKHEN," zogt er

00:10:12.523 --> 00:10:15.132
"do, do vet zayn undzer sof?"

00:10:16.658 --> 00:10:20.634
zey hobn gekent e- alemen oysshisn, in a vald, ober s'iz

00:10:21.315 --> 00:10:25.471
zog ikh "makh nit keyn panik. keyner veyst nit vos

00:10:25.471 --> 00:10:26.945
un me darf vartn."

00:10:28.285 --> 00:10:32.548
nor az mir, in der nakht fun ershtn oyfn tsveytn

00:10:33.887 --> 00:10:35.129
may

00:10:36.925 --> 00:10:43.112
i- mir flegn geyn zeyer fil, un geyn alts oyf hekher, zaynen shoyn geven

00:10:43.185 --> 00:10:44.461
in di Alpn

00:10:47.083 --> 00:10:50.806
iz ⟨mir hobn zikh⟩ avekgeleygt UNK un hiltserne

00:10:51.285 --> 00:10:53.877
shikh hob ikh

00:10:53.884 --> 00:10:56.055
un dray PORTYANKAs hob ikh

00:10:56.112 --> 00:10:58.232
hob ikh zikh avekgeleygt, un ikh bin ayngeshlofn.

00:11:00.077 --> 00:11:02.703
ver s'hot geshlofn un ver s'hot nit geshlofn

00:11:04.009 --> 00:11:06.112
ober in der fri, az ikh hob zikh oyfgekhapt

00:11:06.642 --> 00:11:08.275
iz nit geven nit keyn

00:11:08.275 --> 00:11:11.597
bavakhung, nit keyn hint, nit keyn

00:11:12.413 --> 00:11:13.807
mir zaynen geven fray

00:11:15.653 --> 00:11:16.794
in di Alpn.

00:11:18.083 --> 00:11:19.275
in der heykh.

00:11:21.947 --> 00:11:26.261
in a por sho arum ⟨es⟩ zaynen gekumen fun dorf, fun untn

00:11:26.301 --> 00:11:27.493
iz gekumen

00:11:27.904 --> 00:11:32.707
etlekhe eltere daytshn vos me nemt nit in armey. zaynen geven mit biksn

00:11:34.013 --> 00:11:35.205
un zey hobn gezogt

00:11:35.430 --> 00:11:36.993
"ir zayt fray.

00:11:37.978 --> 00:11:41.111
ayere ba- ayere bavakhung iz avek shoyn.

00:11:41.539 --> 00:11:44.705
ir m- mit undz lozt zikh arop in dorf

00:11:45.133 --> 00:11:48.131
un ir vet vartn. dortn veln kumen amerikaner."

00:11:51.040 --> 00:11:53.143
zaynen mir mit zey gegangen

00:11:53.267 --> 00:11:58.576
un zey hobn gezogt vartn biz fir a zeyger. fir a zeyger vet da- veln dokh kumen di amerikaner.

00:12:00.203 --> 00:12:03.741
nit y- ale zaynen distsiplinirt vi LEMKHENen.

00:12:04.000 --> 00:12:07.268
un zey hobn n- nit gegangen in keyn, di hayzer.

00:12:07.408 --> 00:12:09.072
zaynen gegangen arum.

00:12:09.754 --> 00:12:10.856
un vu

00:12:10.856 --> 00:12:11.733
un

00:12:11.733 --> 00:12:16.852
zaynen efsher arayn in vos far a hayzer UNK m'hot zey mekhabed geven mit vos kh'veys nit

00:12:17.095 --> 00:12:19.505
alnfals iz shoyn geven fraye mentshn

00:12:19.505 --> 00:12:22.635
vayle di vos zaynen geven bay undz zaynen gekumen nokh mit biksn.

00:12:24.418 --> 00:12:27.787
nor a zeyger fir oder shpeter a bisl vi fir

00:12:27.895 --> 00:12:31.989
zaynen gef- iz geforn amerikaner militer.

00:12:33.295 --> 00:12:34.571
iz geforn

00:12:35.016 --> 00:12:36.275
hastik

00:12:36.636 --> 00:12:40.055
un zey hobn, loyt undzere begodim hobn zey gezen az dos iz

00:12:41.378 --> 00:12:43.093
hobn zey gevorfn undz

00:12:44.083 --> 00:12:47.919
pushkes konservn, shokolad, konfekt

00:12:48.432 --> 00:12:51.058
ober zikh nit opgeshtelt oyf keyn minut nit.

00:12:51.891 --> 00:12:53.741
zey hobn zikh zeyer gehaylt

00:12:53.983 --> 00:12:57.031
tsu farkhapn mer teritorye

00:12:57.763 --> 00:13:00.153
es zol nit araynfaln tsu di rusn.

00:13:04.007 --> 00:13:08.624
un di, di dorfishe hobn gezen az di amerikaner shteln zikh nit op

00:13:10.825 --> 00:13:13.049
un amerikaner zaynen farbaygeforn

00:13:13.049 --> 00:13:15.830
a hipsh bisl zaynen geforn, ober alts

00:13:15.904 --> 00:13:21.348
hoyle militer un hoyle uniformirte

00:13:23.498 --> 00:13:26.749
hobn, hobn mir nit gevust vos tsu ton.

00:13:26.856 --> 00:13:32.452
hobn di dorfishe UNK ba- baklert az me ken dokh di mentshn nit lozn

00:13:32.610 --> 00:13:34.055
azoy

00:13:34.146 --> 00:13:36.823
hobn di dorfishe gegebn a kuk

00:13:36.880 --> 00:13:39.962
un tsvishn undzere hot zikh ayngefunen a por

00:13:39.968 --> 00:13:42.949
vos kene- ka- katsovim vos kenen

00:13:43.005 --> 00:13:44.720
arbetn oyf a ku

00:13:44.811 --> 00:13:47.741
un m'hot avekgekoylet di ku, un m'hot gemakht

00:13:48.000 --> 00:13:49.515
aropgeshundn

00:13:49.515 --> 00:13:53.748
un m'hot gegebn a groysn kesl, un m'hot ge- oysgekokht fleysh

00:13:55.543 --> 00:13:57.882
un m'hot avekgeshtelt etlekhe punktn.

00:13:58.058 --> 00:14:00.819
in eyn punkt hot men mir avekgeshtelt oyf a

00:14:01.078 --> 00:14:02.709
oyf aroysgeber

00:14:03.643 --> 00:14:09.143
un i- ale aroysgeber hot men ongezogt az zey zoln zogn az me zol zikh nit tsukhapn tsu fil mit

00:14:09.143 --> 00:14:10.993
ken fardarbn dem mogn.

00:14:14.680 --> 00:14:19.146
nu, mir hobn gegesn, i- nit mit eyn mol

